noback sign \x2571 345 в•ұ   right-leaning single solid diagonal line segment   # using noback to avoid conflict with "ar" contraction
noback sign \x2572 126 в•І   left-leaning single solid diagonal line segment   # using noback to avoid conflict with "gh" contraction


#   Unicode:  Geometric Shapes

sign \x25a0 456-1246-3456-145 в–    filled (solid) square
sign \x25a1 1246-3456-145 в–Ў   square
sign \x25a7 46-1246-3456-145 в–§   shaded square (upper left to lower right)
sign \x25b2 456-1246-3456-14 в–І   filled (solid) (equilateral) triangle
sign \x25b3 1246-3456-14 в–і   regular (equilateral) triangle
sign \x25cb 1246-123456 в—Ӣ   circle
sign \x25cd 46-1246-123456 в—Қ   shaded circle
sign \x25aa 456-256 в–Ә
noback sign \x25cf 5-35 в—Ҹ   black circle   # not representing filled circle shape as it is mostly used in password fields to represent hidden characters


