uplow \x040e\x04e5 45-346-13456 РҺСһ
uplow \x04aa\x04ab 45-12346-14 ТӘТ«
uplow \x04b0\x04b1 4-25-13456 Т°Тұ
uplow \x04d0\x04d1 4-346-1 УҗУ‘
uplow \x04d2\x04d3 45-25-1 У’У“
uppercase \x04d4 1-6-45-235-15 У”
lowercase \x04d5 1-45-235-15 У•
