# Common combinations of one word contractions with slash
word af/pГҘ 356-34-1234
word af/pГҘ 356-34-68-1234
word du/i 145-34-24
word du/i 145-34-68-24
word eller/og 15-34-14
word eller/og 15-34-68-14
