math                   \x00f7 5-256                        Г· DIVISION SIGN
noback math            \x2236 5-256                        вҲ¶ RATIO
noback math            \x2044 34                           вҒ„ FRACTION SLASH
noback math            \x2215 34                           вҲ• DIVISION SLASH


